02:12:54,551 --> 02:12:56,172
that's fine".

1054
02:13:10,466 --> 02:13:13,219
You have until tomorrow to vote.

1055
02:13:13,694 --> 02:13:14,671
Vote!

1056
02:13:14,696 --> 02:13:16,727
And win a vacation on the Moon.

1057
02:13:16,752 --> 02:13:18,171
For the whole family.

1058
02:13:18,976 --> 02:13:20,906
Win a trip to the Moon!

1059
02:13:21,390 --> 02:13:24,169
Take a swing at a fabulous golf vacation.

1060
02:13:37,224 --> 02:13:40,157
Have they announced
the results of the voting?

1061
02:13:41,187 --> 02:13:42,582
I'm sorry.

1062
02:13:42,607 --> 02:13:45,302
At my age,

1063
02:13:45,327 --> 02:13:49,118
the candles cost more than a cake.

1064
02:13:53,229 --> 02:13:55,683
I'm not afraid of dying.

1065
02:13:55,987 --> 02:13:59,049
I'm afraid I haven't been alive enough!

1066
02:14:02,455 --> 02:14:06,701
It should be written on every
schoolroom blackboard.

1067
02:14:08,490 --> 02:14:11,235
Life is a playground.

1068
02:14:12,804 --> 02:14:14,726
Or nothing.

1069
02:14:21,250 --> 02:14:21,951
Nemo. Leave.

1070
02:14:21,976 --> 02:14:23,614
NOW

1071
02:14:26,087 --> 02:14:29,302
Nemo. Leave. NOW

1072
02:14:36,377 --> 02:14:37,378
Nemo!

1073
02:14:54,341 --> 02:14:57,937
NEMO, READ THE NEWS.

1074
02:15:08,696 --> 02:15:10,438
Tragic car accident
on a country road

1075
02:15:12,308 --> 02:15:14,451
Nemo turn to page 5

1076
02:15:15,274 --> 02:15:17,643
Nemo look at the
end of the street

1077
02:15:20,580 --> 02:15:23,805
NEMO CALL
123 581 1321

1078
02:15:32,459 --> 02:15:35,405
<i>- Hello, who is this?
- Hello, who is this?</i>

1079
02:15:36,104 --> 02:15:37,283
<i>Who is this?</i>

1080
02:15:38,381 --> 02:15:39,849
I was told to call this number.

1081
02:15:40,352 --> 02:15:42,136
My name is Nemo Nobody.

1082
02:15:44,120 --> 02:15:45,674
Is this some kind of a joke?

1083
02:15:46,239 --> 02:15:48,073
No. No, I...

1084
02:15:52,936 --> 02:15:54,274
<i>- Operator?
- Yes?</i>

1085
02:15:54,299 --> 02:15:58,198
I'd like the address to
123 581 1321.

1086
02:15:59,196 --> 02:16:00,440
<i>One moment please.</i>

1087
02:16:02,214 --> 02:16:04,417
<i>12358 Alleway Street.</i>

1088
02:16:32,864 --> 02:16:34,539
<i>Hello, Nemo.</i>

1089
02:16:35,086 --> 02:16:37,139
<i>I'm glad you found me.</i>

1090
02:16:37,798 --> 02:16:40,788
<i>All of this must seem
very complicated to you,</i>

1091
02:16:40,813 --> 02:16:43,308
<i>but it's simpler than you think.</i>

1092
02:16:43,882 --> 02:16:46,218
<i>Careful with the chair.
It is damaged.</i>

1093
02:16:52,898 --> 02:16:56,118
<i>- Are you alright?
- I'm fine.</i>

1094
02:16:58,274 --> 02:17:00,352
<i>I should have
warned you earlier but...</i>

1095
02:17:00,592 --> 02:17:03,204
<i>I couldn't
because of the transcript.</i>

1096
02:17:03,430 --> 02:17:04,430
The transcript?

1097
02:17:05,046 --> 02:17:08,281
<i>The text of our conversation!</i>

1098
02:17:10,609 --> 02:17:13,510
<i>- You can you hear me!
- What you are living now...</i>

1099
02:17:14,367 --> 02:17:15,846
<i>is the past.</i>

1100
02:17:16,973 --> 02:17:18,732
<i>At least, for me.</i>

1101
02:17:20,691 --> 02:17:22,095
<i>I am you...</i>

1102
02:17:23,057 --> 02:17:25,585
<i>70 years older.</i>

1103
02:17:27,257 --> 02:17:31,353
<i>Everything you say, I said
myself when I was young.</i>

1104
02:17:31,567 --> 02:17:35,222
<i>I only had to transcribe
our conversation.</i>

1105
02:17:35,970 --> 02:17:38,313
<i>It's all written right here.</i>

1106
02:17:38,338 --> 02:17:39,847
<i>- I can't...
- Believe it?</i>

1107
02:17:42,117 --> 02:17:43,502
<i>For me...</i>

1108
02:17:44,343 --> 02:17:46,551
<i>...time is inverted.</i>

1109
02:17:47,267 --> 02:17:49,806
<i>I start at the end of the story</i>

1110
02:17:49,831 --> 02:17:51,808
<i>and go toward the beginning.</i>

1111
02:17:52,715 --> 02:17:54,324
I don't understand.

1112
02:17:54,349 --> 02:17:55,951
<i>In this life here,</i>

1113
02:17:56,686 --> 02:17:58,819
you don't exist.

1114
02:17:58,844 --> 02:18:00,662
<i>I don't know why...</i>

1115
02:18:01,081 --> 02:18:03,309
<i>Only the Architect knows.</i>

1116
02:18:04,949 --> 02:18:05,942
The Architect?

1117
02:18:07,098 --> 02:18:08,447
<i>The child...</i>

1118
02:18:09,472 --> 02:18:12,238
<i>The one running after the train.</i>

1119
02:18:13,977 --> 02:18:16,700
<i>Maybe your parents never met.</i>

1120
02:18:20,972 --> 02:18:25,829
<i>Maybe your father died
in a sledging accident.</i>

1121
02:18:27,541 --> 02:18:29,850
<i>Maybe you were one
of the vast majority</i>

1122
02:18:29,875 --> 02:18:34,605
<i>of those whose genetic code did not
reach its final destination.</i>

1123
02:18:38,022 --> 02:18:39,580
<i>Maybe when she died...</i>

1124
02:18:40,534 --> 02:18:42,212
<i>A prehistoric woman...</i>

1125
02:18:42,461 --> 02:18:46,457
<i>She rolled off the line of heritance
to which you belong.</i>

1126
02:18:47,823 --> 02:18:49,357
<i>So for this world...</i>

1127
02:18:52,353 --> 02:18:54,624
<i>You don't exist.</i>

1128
02:18:56,125 --> 02:18:59,081
<i>If the Anna's calculations are correct,</i>

1129
02:18:59,795 --> 02:19:06,411
<i>you need to stay alive
until 2092, February 12.</i>

1130
02:19:07,324 --> 02:19:10,160
<i>5:50 AM.</i>

1131
02:19:42,714 --> 02:19:45,131
I'm sorry, I don't know how long
we haven't been recording.

1132
02:19:45,266 --> 02:19:47,659
I have to submit my story
by tomorrow morning.

1133
02:19:50,101 --> 02:19:52,373
Everything that you say
is contradictory.

1134
02:19:53,886 --> 02:19:57,452
You can't have been in one place
and another at the same time.

1135
02:19:58,301 --> 02:20:02,496
You mean to say
we have to make choices?

1136
02:20:02,973 --> 02:20:04,542
Of all those lives, which one...

1137
02:20:05,996 --> 02:20:07,373
Which one is the right one?

1138
02:20:08,331 --> 02:20:12,022
Each of these lives
is the right one.

1139
02:20:13,647 --> 02:20:18,336
Every path is the right path.

1140
02:20:21,906 --> 02:20:26,209
"Everything could have been
anything else...

1141
02:20:27,644 --> 02:20:32,185
and it would have just
as much meaning."

1142
02:20:34,372 --> 02:20:36,768
Tennessee Williams.

1143
02:20:38,521 --> 02:20:40,779
You're too young for that.

1144
02:20:41,142 --> 02:20:42,781
You can't be dead
and still be here.

1145
02:20:44,423 --> 02:20:45,527
You can't not exist.

1146
02:20:52,211 --> 02:20:53,743
Is there life after death?

1147
02:20:57,259 --> 02:20:58,677
After death...

1148
02:21:02,261 --> 02:21:08,236
How can you be so sure
you even exist?

1149
02:21:18,395 --> 02:21:21,103
You don't exist.

1150
02:21:22,638 --> 02:21:24,242
Neither do I.

1151
02:21:27,416 --> 02:21:33,697
We only live in the imagination
of a nine year old child.

1152
02:21:34,514 --> 02:21:38,756
We are imagined
by a nine year old child,

1153
02:21:39,682 --> 02:21:42,619
faced with an impossible choice.

1154
02:21:52,363 --> 02:21:53,730
Run! Run!

1155
02:21:59,992 --> 02:22:01,196
Nemo!

1156
02:22:06,823 --> 02:22:08,264
Run!

1157
02:22:13,178 --> 02:22:14,282
Run, Nemo!

1158
02:22:17,248 --> 02:22:18,558
Nemo!

1159
02:22:27,390 --> 02:22:28,537
I love you.

1160
02:22:29,373 --> 02:22:30,374
Anna!

1161
02:22:43,537 --> 02:22:44,538
Nemo!

1162
02:22:54,162 --> 02:22:55,732
You're the one I love.

1163
02:23:11,697 --> 02:23:12,860
In chess,

1164
02:23:15,251 --> 02:23:17,970
it's called Zugzwang,

1165
02:23:19,540 --> 02:23:21,937
when the only viable move

1166
02:23:27,439 --> 02:23:29,475
is not to move.

1167
02:23:39,367 --> 02:23:40,909
Come see.

1168
02:24:04,663 --> 02:24:05,482
It's the sea.

1169
02:24:06,500 --> 02:24:09,470
The child is taking it apart.

1170
02:24:10,836 --> 02:24:13,094
He doesn't need it anymore.

1171
02:24:14,314 --> 02:24:18,093
Before, he was unable
to make a choice

1172
02:24:19,010 --> 02:24:21,453
'cause he didn't know
what would happen.

1173
02:24:22,252 --> 02:24:25,080
Now that he knows
what will happen,

1174
02:24:27,230 --> 02:24:29,834
he is unable to make a choice.

1175
02:25:35,568 --> 02:25:37,209
Thank you, thank you!

1176
02:25:37,662 --> 02:25:38,474
Thank you.

1177
02:26:14,994 --> 02:26:22,209
This is the most beautiful day
of my life.

1178
02:26:29,843 --> 02:26:30,643
Anna.

1179
02:26:34,508 --> 02:26:35,465
Anna.

